    "en": {
      "title": "Meals are given to begging or school children",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "\"Giving food to children in times of need. What's wrong with that?\" Education Minister Susil Premjayantha asked in Parliament.",
        "He said this while clarifying the issue raised in the Parliament yesterday regarding receiving a stock of food from America as aid.",
        "He also mentioned that he has been wearing black suits since before 1985. That some persons were in the dock when they represented the defendants in court.",
        "He further said that when he became the minister, he first thought about the process of providing lunch for school children."
      ],
